  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK357">
<l>ōrttuḷḷa muḷḷa tuṇari ṉorutalaiyāp</l>
<l>pērttuḷḷa vēṇṭā piṟappu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let it not be thought that there is another birth for him whose mind having thoroughly considered (all it has been taught) has known the True Being.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
